section near downtown Louisville
and drove about 100 pers ons from

Mayor William Cowger called
it one of the worst fires in the
city's history.


The homes we're small, wooden
buildings.

fire has not been determined,
but said residents saw three
small boys playing near the ware
house about 80 minutes before the
fire was sighted.


No one was reported seriously
injured. Two firemen we're over
come by smoke. Three women

White, administrator, Mt. Norris
Park Hospital, has been nomina-
ted for membership in the Ameri-
can College of Hospital Admin
strators.


Mr.. White became administra-
tor of Mt. Norris Park Hospital
In 1860. A native New Yorker,
he is familiar with, and deeply
concerned about the problems of
our people everywhere, espe-
cially education. He believes this
is the key to the colution Of most

the Job of administrator keeps
